name: Isak Harouni
note:
Сompany Name: SEO Traffic Online, https://seotrafficonline.com/
Contact Person: Isak Harouni
Product: the variety of website oriented tasks, like to boost up the sales, rankings in the SEO, SEO visibility etc. every website needs the consulting services to jump up the stable position in the world of the internet, SEO consulting is the essential component to promote the offers and publicize the brand all over the world. 
Services Provided: consulting, content writing, e-reputation
Country-Location: Israel 
Target Audience: people who want to modify their website content
Immediate Requirement: SEO, wordpress, developers, to develop crm system 
Next Step: send all information, send links to possible candidates, we will organise an interview
Next Contact Date: April 1 11:00 am - interview

Fresh results
SM:Uliana
We interviewed:
Roman Batrak 901 - PPC, SEO,  really experienced, answered all the questions.
Artem 37863 - SEO, nice English, described his experience, answered the questions, has some mistakes but is confident in himself
Yana 841- junior SEO manager an SMM manager, know WordPress, confidence, nice English.
Maria https://rh-s.com/content-manager/mariia-c/ - SMM facebook manager, optimize her friend, tatoo website, they have 100k subscribers, confident, good English.
Oksana https://rh-s.com/content-managers/oksana-m/ - SMM manager, build marketing strategies, answered the questions, good English
Result:
Isak told that the knowledge of our managers is not enough, he needs juniors but more specified in SEO.
So if we will have new candidates in SEO. Isak is also interested in Roman as a PPC manager, so he will probably set one more interview with him if there will be a need from his PPC department. In addition, Isak has one more need in PHP and API integration.
Next step: send CV`s of developers by mail, Isak will discuss the PPC issue internally and we will set interview by mail.

FRESH RESULTS
RESULTS

Immediate Requirement: Isak is looking for a developer Wordpress with knowledge of API because they have a big project to handle and to move forward with. It’s devided on 2 parts:
1. https://dataforseo.com/ they are creating a kind of platform that is going to analyze at real time any link that you add to this platform(registration will be needed from the user’s side and from the admin’s side) Look and fill of back office are very important, they should be changed accordingly.

2. Second part will be a kind of tool like those semrush.com, ahrefs.com, moz.com Isak wants to create 1 only platform that will include data of those 3 one. It’s a kind of Business model where companies will pay monthly fee to get those information.

Also Isak needs somebody who will help with SEO (level should be at least medium, not just content writing).

Next Step: send CV’s of candidates and examples of their works.

Next Contact Date: keep in touch by email.

SM Anna
